{"id": 5361, "title": "Ticket #5361: Remove pool password file during stack deletion.", "description": "<blockquote>\nWe currently delete the pool password file when <code>condor_annex</code> terminates, which causes grief for Spot instances.  After discussing it with JimK, we'll just leave the pool password in the private S3 bucket until the stack terminates, instead.\n\n<p>We need to (a) remove the pool password file on stack deletion and (b) not delete the pool password on termination of <code>condor_annex</code>.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Nov-10 15:58</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/9412742e5cfed4fed9c3e420360c966f26f7451b\">[46239]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5361\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5361'); return false;\" title=\"Remove pool password file during stack deletion.\">#5361</a></span>) Improve error reporting from clean-up script.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2015-Nov-10 14:23</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/5bb6edbd7682ed26fb21ddc565521600bb61d79f\">[46238]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=5361\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('5361'); return false;\" title=\"Remove pool password file during stack deletion.\">#5361</a></spa